  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0dad\u0dca\u0daf\u0dc5 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Suspicious of someone with ivory",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 42-year-old man has been arrested in the Kalady, Vellore area in Batticaloa for allegedly killing elephants and possessing a pair of tusks, police said.",
        "According to information received by the STF Ampara Camp, on the instructions of the Commanding Officer of the STF, DIG Waruna Jayasundara, the Second Commanding Officer of the Base, Inspector TBRP A team of officers including Siriwardena arrested the ivory tusks during a raid carried out in the Brownry Road area in Batticaloa.",
        "The Special Task Force (STF) has been conducting routine operations to nab ivory and pearl smugglers in and around World Heritage Sites and government reserves."
      ],
